Package ca.ualberta.cmput301f14t16.easya.Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    The Answer class extends the Topic class, providing no extra functionality.
    Content
    The Content class is an abstract class that provides several utility methods to its subclasses.
    GeneralHelper
    Provides a helper class containing general-use methods for repeated use across several classes.
    MainModel<V extends MainView>
    Provides a method of interacting with the data created and stored by the application.
    Pending
    Pending is cache like buffer used to store a Question, Answer or Reply object that has not yet been submitted.
    Question
    The Question class is an extension of the Content class, that provides functions for associating and retrieving relevant Answer and Reply objects.
    QuestionList
    Provides a lightweight implementation of Question, to be used as a condensed view of a Question object when several such objects are stored in list form.
    Queue
    Created by Cauani on 2014-10-25.
    Reply
    The Reply class extends the Content class, providing no extra functionality.
    Sort  
    Topic
    Topic extends Content, providing added functionality to suit more specific purposes.
    User
    Provides a method of storing and accessing all data relevant to a single user, uniquely identified by the User.id field.
